text: Jannik Schuster (born 16 May 2006) is an Austrian professional football player. He plays as a defender for 2. Liga club FC Liefering. He also plays for FC Red Bull Salzburg U19 in the UEFA Youth League. ==Careeer == Schuster began his career at SV Mieming. In February 2020 he moved to the FC Red Bull Salzburg academy. There he went through all age levels. In October 2023 he made his debut for FC Liefering in the 2nd league. On 21 October he was in the starting line-up against SK Sturm Graz II on the eleventh matchday of the 2023/24 season. ==International == Schuster played for an Austrian youth national team for the first time on 6 April 2022 versus Czech Republic. transfermarkt.at In September 2023 he made his debut for the U-18 team against Saudi Arabia. transfermarkt.at ==References== Category:2006 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian footballers Category:FC Liefering players Category:Austrian football defenders
